{"title":"金色的斗篷","authors":["袁万祥"],"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":11,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的斗篷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江苏射阳县射中电影放映队　袁万祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏日水乡浪千重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声飘自绿浪中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"循着歌声放眼望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先见顶顶竹斗篷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坝口才与斗篷别，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水稻田里巧相逢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为找书记走全队——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一色斗篷在移动！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小憩坐在田埂上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"取下斗篷扇凉风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘小伙方有别，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部社员仍相同……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞美你呵竹斗篷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任凭日烤劈雷轰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万难排在斗篷外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收握在手心中！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水乡勇创大寨县，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各行各业都支农。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——今年斗篷空前多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光闪闪遍田垄……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}